# GPU Experiments — Implementation Plan

Five new experiments to strengthen the paper. ONER/UCAD comparison is excluded (requires external codebases and significant reimplementation effort).

## Proposed Changes

### Experiment Overview

| ID | Experiment | What Changes | GPU Time Est. |
|---|---|---|---|
| E8 | **k ablation** | Override `config.scoring.k` for k ∈ {1,3,5,9,15,25} | ~18 min (6×3min) |
| E9 | **Task ordering sensitivity** | Shuffle category order in 3 permutations | ~9 min (3×3min) |
| E10 | **Statistical significance** | Run E1 with 3 seeds [42, 123, 456] | ~9 min (3×3min) |
| E11 | **Layer selection ablation** | Re-extract features with different layer combos | ~2hrs extraction + 4×3min runs |
| E12 | **P-AUROC** | Cache GT masks, compute pixel-level AUROC | ~5 min (rerun E1 with mask eval) |

---

### New Script

#### [NEW] [run_new_experiments.py](file:///c:/Users/pramo/.gemini/antigravity/playground/stellar-equinox/scripts/run_new_experiments.py)

Unified script with `--only E8 E9 ...` support, modeled after [run_all_experiments.py](file:///c:/Users/pramo/.gemini/antigravity/playground/stellar-equinox/scripts/run_all_experiments.py).

**E8: k ablation** — Loops k ∈ {1, 3, 5, 9, 15, 25}, overrides `config['scoring']['k']`, runs E1 pipeline with cached features. No new feature extraction needed. Saves to `results/E8_k_ablation_k{N}/results.json`.

**E9: Task ordering** — Creates 3 shuffled permutations of the 15 MVTec categories, groups into 5 tasks of 3, runs E1 pipeline for each. Uses same cached features. Saves to `results/E9_ordering_{seed}/results.json`.

**E10: Statistical significance** — Runs E1 pipeline 3 times with seeds [42, 123, 456] for coreset random seed. Reports mean ± std. Saves to `results/E10_seed_{seed}/results.json`.

**E11: Layer ablation** — Needs 3 additional feature extractions:
- Layers [6, 11] → `data/features/dinov2_vitb14_l6_11/`
- Layers [7, 9, 11] → `data/features/dinov2_vitb14_l7_9_11/`
- Layers [11] → `data/features/dinov2_vitb14_l11/`

Then runs E1 pipeline with each. The existing [7, 11] serves as the 4th config.

**E12: P-AUROC** — Requires:

