## Execution Order

1. **E8** (k ablation) — fastest, no dependencies
2. **E9** (task ordering) — fast, no dependencies  
3. **E10** (statistical significance) — fast, no dependencies
4. **E12** (P-AUROC) — moderate, needs mask caching first
5. **E11** (layer ablation) — slowest, needs new feature extraction

